{"id":2782,"date":"2019-02-02T12:42:51","date_gmt":"2019-02-02T11:42:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=2782"},"modified":"2019-04-14T08:41:05","modified_gmt":"2019-04-14T06:41:05","slug":"shakespeare-in-the-bois-de-boulogne-the-merry-wives-of-windsor","status":"publish","type":"tribe_events","link":"https:\/\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/event\/shakespeare-in-the-bois-de-boulogne-the-merry-wives-of-windsor\/","title":{"rendered":"Shakespeare in the Bois de Boulogne: The Merry Wives of Windsor"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2><strong>Tue 4th June &#8211; <em>Shakespeare in the Shakespeare Garden, Bois de Boulogne\u00c2\u00a0(Pr\u00c3\u00a9 Catalan)<\/p>\n<p>The Merry Wives of Windsor\u00c2\u00a0<\/em>by the Tower Theatre Company<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><em><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-3284\" src=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Merry-Wives-of-Windsor.jpeg?resize=226%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"226\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Merry-Wives-of-Windsor.jpeg?resize=226%2C300&amp;ssl=1 226w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Merry-Wives-of-Windsor.jpeg?resize=350%2C465&amp;ssl=1 350w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/Merry-Wives-of-Windsor.jpeg?w=463&amp;ssl=1 463w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 226px) 100vw, 226px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/>The Women of Windsor take on Sir John Falstaff and his cronies, in a garden party extravaganza of Shakespeare&#8217;s classic comedy. Laundry baskets at the ready!<\/p>\n<p>Ford and Page have a problem. Sir John Falstaff is broke, and plans on seducing them in order to get to their husbands&#8217; money. But Falstaff is a creep, and the Wives are cunning. They&#8217;ll outmanoeuvre his tricks and humiliate him instead. In a town and society with men at the centre, the women of Windsor must come together, and teach them all a lesson they&#8217;ll never forget.<\/em><\/p>\n<div><strong><em>To book your tickets<\/em><\/strong>\n<\/div>\n<div><em>Tickets are \u00e2\u201a\u00ac22 per person (\u00e2\u201a\u00ac12 for children under 14). This includes the play as well as strawberries and champagne at the interval.<\/p>\n<p>To book, please download the<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>\u00c2\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/cambridgesocietyofparis.us12.list-manage.com\/track\/click?u=1d89c83f7c6d342f93635573f&amp;id=1d74da9122&amp;e=a3b087f68c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">reservation form<\/a><\/strong><\/span> and send it\u00c2\u00a0to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><a href=\"mailto:crhohler38@gmail.com?subject=Shakespeare%202019\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Clare Hohler<\/a><\/strong><\/span>, either by email or post as indicated\u00c2\u00a0on the reservation form. \u00c2\u00a0Tickets will be issued at the gate from 6.30pm. but if you would like prior confirmation of your booking please request this by email to <a href=\"mailto:crhohler38@gmail.com?subject=Shakespeare%202019\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Clare<\/a>.<\/em><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tue 4th June &#8211; Shakespeare in the Shakespeare Garden, Bois de Boulogne\u00c2\u00a0(Pr\u00c3\u00a9 Catalan) The Merry Wives of Windsor\u00c2\u00a0by the Tower Theatre Company The Women of Windsor take on Sir John &hellip; <\/p>\n<p class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cambridgesocietyofparis.com\/event\/shakespeare-in-the-bois-de-boulogne-the-merry-wives-of-windsor\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> &#8220;Shakespeare in the Bois de Boulogne: The Merry Wives of Windsor&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":1953,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed",